Second, and this is to ST and DBC, I did not say that everyone was at the extreme.  I specifically said that people were not at the extremes.  I was implying that the shape would be more like a double bell curve.  Kinda like what you see in courses where half the class copied homework assignments from the other half.  Half the class gets Cs because they bomb the exams(cause they only copied and didn't understand) while the other half got As(cause they understood the material).  Relatively no A+ or F marks.  Relatively no fanatics. <br>
